• Oversee all marketing analytics and optimization strategies.;
• Lead our acquisition efforts and strategic roadmap for social, display, search and affiliate marketing.;
• Partner with publishing teams to drive growth and ensure campaigns are in alignment with brand positioning and strategic
goals.;
• Continuously work to improve ROI through A/B testing, channel analysis, daily monitoring/reporting, etc.;
• Create and manage attribution model and efficiency of digital marketing spend.;
• Proactively stay abreast of industry trends and search for new opportunities to grow channels and refine strategies and tactics.;

